1.11 Decision-Making Framework

Instead of making technology choices based on trends, we'll evaluate them consistently. For every significant decision, we'll ask:

Business Value – Does this directly help Jobfynder's mission?
Operational Impact – Can we run and support it with our current team?
Complexity – Is there a simpler solution?
Scalability – Will it still be appropriate if we grow 10×?
Maintainability – Will a new engineer understand it in six months?
Cost – Does the value justify the infrastructure and operational cost?
Observability – Can we monitor and troubleshoot it effectively?
Exit Strategy – If we need to replace it later, how difficult will that be?

This framework will help us evaluate everything from AI models to databases to third-party services.